1303
01:13:33,490 --> 01:13:34,323
- Marta.

1304
01:13:35,920 --> 01:13:38,010
- I'm not having my party.

1305
01:13:38,010 --> 01:13:40,560
It's just not that important
anymore, all right?

1306
01:13:40,560 --> 01:13:41,640
- All right.

1307
01:13:41,640 --> 01:13:43,040
- It's okay, Marta.

1308
01:13:43,040 --> 01:13:44,180
- Of course it is.

1309
01:13:44,180 --> 01:13:46,433
- Hey, Marta, you wanna
see something funny?

