01:14:07,897 --> 01:14:08,730
- No, don't.

1323
01:14:08,730 --> 01:14:10,128
- Three.

1324
01:14:10,128 --> 01:14:10,961
- No!

1325
01:14:33,649 --> 01:14:36,641
