1332
01:14:48,520 --> 01:14:50,080
but I can't find the file.

1333
01:14:50,080 --> 01:14:52,310
- That's no surprise, look at this mess.

1334
01:14:52,310 --> 01:14:53,700
Whose was it?

1335
01:14:53,700 --> 01:14:55,513
- A man named Arturo Montoya.

1336
01:14:59,480 --> 01:15:03,270
- Marta, your father
withdrew his application.

1337
01:15:03,270 --> 01:15:04,103
- Why?

1338
01:15:07,230 --> 01:15:09,113
- He feels cornered.

1339
