1344
01:15:24,440 --> 01:15:25,273
- Can't you help?

1345
01:15:25,273 --> 01:15:27,260
Isn't there anything you can do?

1346
01:15:27,260 --> 01:15:29,750
- I'm afraid it's out of my hands.

1347
01:15:29,750 --> 01:15:31,350
