way he can qualify for amnesty.

1399
01:19:51,730 --> 01:19:53,030
- So what?

1400
01:19:53,030 --> 01:19:54,820
- I can do that for him.

1401
01:19:54,820 --> 01:19:57,030
I just have to get
signatures at his old jobs

1402
