1406
01:20:07,732 --> 01:20:10,149
(tire thuds)

1407
01:20:15,055 --> 01:20:18,162
(tire thuds)

1408
01:20:18,162 --> 01:20:21,412
(light dramatic music)

1409
01:20:23,510 --> 01:20:25,730
- You said, "You could talk to me."

1410
01:20:25,730 --> 01:20:27,230
Well, you said some things to me too

1411
