1412
01:20:29,110 --> 01:20:29,943
- Like what?

1413
01:20:31,250 --> 01:20:34,150
- You told me, "That my family's
the best thing I've got."

1414
01:20:35,924 --> 01:20:38,124
And I'm gonna show my
father I believe that.

1415
01:20:46,620 --> 01:20:47,470
- Chauffeur, huh?

1416
01:20:51,630 --> 01:20:53,410
